flowchart TD
    A[User prompt] --> B[Initial agent claims]
    B --> C{Missing required fields?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Request missing data]
    D --> E[Downgrade confidence]
    E --> F[Suggest additional agents]
    C -- No --> G{Cross-domain intent under-covered?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Expand agent scope]
    H --> I[Re-score claims]
    G -- No --> I
    I --> J[Arbitration ready]
